    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Karolus divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs>
                        augustus anno imperii eius quinto, atque filio eius Lodovico similiter
                        quinto, die sesto mensis octuber, indictione quarta, <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47">sanctorum omninum
                            apostolorum et Christi confessoris Silvestri</orgName> siti <rs
                            key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/38" key="#City_territory">Motinensi</placeName> loco
                        qui vocatur <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15"
                            >Nonantulas</placeName>, in quo domnus <persName key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks" ref="#people/1242"
                            >Theodoricus</persName> vir venerabilis <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse
                        videtur, ego quidem <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/"
                                ><name>Litefredus</name></persName> gloriosissimus <rs key="#Count"
                            >comes</rs> de <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Comitatus" ref="#places/58"><geogName
                                key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/271"
                            >Cremonensis</geogName></placeName> filius bone memorie <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#people/"><name>Liutefrido</name></persName> comitis
                        pro remedio anime mee seu omnium parentorum meorum dono, trado et offero in
                        eodem monasterio nominative <rs key="#Petiae">pecias</rs> quindecim de terra
                        iuris mei proprietatis, que esse videtur in loco et fundo qui dicitur
                            <placeName key="#Petiae" ref="#places/15">Bulgari</placeName> et
                            <placeName key="#Petiae" ref="#places/3682">Nocetulo</placeName> atque
                            <placeName key="#Petiae #Roads" ref="#places/15">Sablone</placeName> qui
                        no(minatur) prope <rs key="#Roads">strata</rs> Papiense. Prima pecia in loco
                            <placeName key="#Petiae" ref="#places/15">Ardole</placeName> est pro
                        mensura iusta iugerum unum, in alio loco insimul una petia iugera tria; alia
                        in Nocetulo iugera due et alia in eodem Nocetulo iugera similiter duo, alia
                        iugerum unum, alia ibi prope iugerum unum, alia in Sablone est perticas
                        triginta, alia ibi prope perticas quatuor, alia perticas octo, alia pecia in
                        loco Bulgari perticas quatuor, alia ibi prope pertica una, alia in eodem
                        fundo perticas duo, alia ibi prope perticas duo, alia … perticas tres, alia
                        perticas octo; similiter dono et offero in eodem monasterio peciam unam de
                        terra foris <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Cremona, que est in loco qui
                            <placeName key="#Petiae">Predario</placeName> dicitur et est pro mensura
                        iuxta iuges tres, perticas quatuor, coeret ei finis a mane heredes quondam
                            <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/">Adelberti</persName> comitis et
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/224">Sancte
                        Marie</orgName>, a meridie fossatum, a mane Sancte Marie et aliquid Sancti
                        Silvestri, a sera ipsius Sacnti Silvestri; similiter dono et offero in eodem
                        monasterio pecias de terra sex in locis et fundis qui <placeName
                            key="#Petiae" ref="#places/15">Septemcani</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Petiae" ref="#places/15">Pipia</placeName>. Prima pecia est pro
                        mensura iusta iuges … sesta pecia in Pipia est pro mensura iuxta iuges sex.
                        … Ego Litefridus manu mea subscripsi. Signum manibus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Arnulfo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Giselberto</name></persName> germanis seu <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Bosio</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Teperto</name></persName> … atque <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Pascale</name></persName> de civitate Cremona qui <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs> rogatis … Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name>Rodevertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii <rs key="#Writer"
                        >scripsi</rs>, post tradita complevi et dedi.</ab>
